<section class="course-overview1">
  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Workspherepulse</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        .about-wrapper {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .about-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .about-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .about-focus {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .about-focus h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .about-list li {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-list li::before {
            content: '\2713'; /* Checkmark symbol */
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .about-cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #b09d5e;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .about-cta h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4E5935;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .about-button:hover {
            background-color: #219150;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .about-wrapper {
                margin: 20px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-wrapper">
        <div class="about-header">
            <h1>About Workspherepulse</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
            <p>We are an online platform for discussing workplace-related events, issues, and situations. Work can provide fulfillment and a sense of purpose, but it also comes with challenges. Our platform serves as a safe space for individuals to share experiences, seek advice, and connect with others.</p>
            <p>We aim to foster a strong community where people feel heard and supported in navigating workplace dynamics.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-focus">
            <h2>Our Focus</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li>Safe and Supportive Environment: A judgment-free space to share experiences.</li>
                <li>Community-Centered: Encouraging interaction and mutual support.</li>
                <li>Information and Resources: Providing guidance for workplace success.</li>
                <li>Forum Discussions: Engaging topics about teams, managers, and workplace dynamics.</li>
                <li>Community Events: Webinars, Q&A sessions, and workshops.</li>
                <li>Accessibility: Open to everyone, regardless of location or background.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-cta">
            <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
            <p>Be part of a community that supports and empowers each other in workplace discussions.</p>
            <a href="/register" class="about-button">Sign Up Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>
